    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What qualities should I consider when selecting between delicate stud earrings and architectural dangle designs?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>The choice reflects your desired level of presence; studs are often masterpieces of focused, micro-detailed brilliance, while our forged dangle creations offer dramatic kinetic energy and movement. </p><p>Our master goldsmiths can advise on which style will best complement your overall ensemble and physical features. We suggest an appointment at our Showroom to view these contrasting Creations in person, allowing us to guide you towards the perfect balance for your aesthetic near {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Are miniature earrings suitable as everyday wear when I am passing through {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Absolutely. For discreet elegance that withstands daily life, Studs are an ideal choice. Many of our micro-pieces feature meticulously set GIA-certified natural diamonds or semi-precious stones, offering lasting brilliance without overwhelming your presence. </p><p>To view the range and determine which pairing will best align with your modern lifestyle in {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}, we welcome you to arrange a private consultation at the Chichester Showroom or via Home Visit.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Can I commission an earring set using my existing family heirlooms for remodelling?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, this is one of our most cherished commissions. We specialise in revitalising inherited jewellery, working diligently to integrate vintage pieces into entirely new, contemporary designs while retaining their precious legacy. </p><p>All restorative work happens meticulously within the secure, trusted environment of our on-site Chichester workshop. To discuss assessing your unique family set from {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}, please book a consultation at the Showroom or via our Home Visit service.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How can I ensure that my earrings are responsibly and ethically sourced?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>At Griffin & Co, ethical intent is woven into every single piece. We guarantee that all materials used, whether Platinum or gold, contain verifiable ethical provenance. </p><p>Furthermore, we extensively practise using 100% recycled precious metals alongside certified natural and lab-grown alternatives. For complete assurance regarding the origin of stones and metals in your pieces commissioned near {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}, please consult with us directly at our Chichester Showroom or via Home Vist.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_BRezAN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "I need earrings that match a specific stone type (e.g., emeralds). Can you guide me through colour matching options?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>The perfect harmony between metal and gemstone is an art form, demanding the expertise of a master craftsman. Whether you are integrating deep emeralds or vibrant sapphires into your design, we have expert knowledge in colour theory and complementary settings. </p><p>We encourage booking a private consultation at our Showroom or by Home Visit; seeing actual examples side-by-side helps us curate the most precise, harmonious aesthetic for your requirements emanating from {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
